text: Michaela Drummond is a track and road racing cyclist from New Zealand. She was born on 5 April 1998. Drummond won bronze medals at the 2017 UCI Track Cycling World Championships and 2019 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. == References == == Other websites == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cyclists Category:New Zealand track cyclists
